2006-03-01  Sebastian Gutsfeld  <segoh@gmx.net>

	*  Release 0.85

2006-02-27  Sebastian Gutsfeld  <segoh@gmx.net>

	* modules/amps mixers/Panning.xml: New module Panning

	* examples/external_square_ringmod.cw: New patch

	* view/controller.py (onMouseMotion): Show range of inVar in statusbar at end of line

	* modules/amps mixers/CrossFader.xml: New module CrossFader

2006-02-24  Sebastian Gutsfeld  <segoh@gmx.net>

	* view/controller.py (onShowModuleXML): Fixed error with module paths with included whitespace.

2006-02-24 Matthias Thar <hiast2@web.de>

	* view/controller.py:
		+ Show valueFrame only when module has inputs.
		+ Additionaly to the description and eventually actual value of 
		  an input show allowed range for input value in statusbar.
		+ onShowModuleXml(): Show module xml file in editor.
	* view/workspace.py:
		+ Add Show Module Xml entry to module menu if external editor is specified.
	* tools/config.py:
		+ specify external editor to use within Cabel.
		+ allow empty values for file/directory chooser vars.
	* view/configurator:
		+ File/Directory chooser bind Kill_Focus Event to textcontrol of 
		  File-/DirBrowseButton control instead of the control itself.
	

2006-02-23  Sebastian Gutsfeld  <segoh@gmx.net>

	*  (Module): New MoogVfc2.xml module (audio input doesn't need an amplitude <= 1)
	(Module): Two new FM patches in example directory.


2006-02-05  Matthias Thar  <hiast2@web.de>

	* tools/config.py (CSound.fillWithDefaults):
		+ added '-+rtmidi=mme' to the standard csound params. MSW plattforms don't need the protmidi plugin
		  as midi suport comes with the standard mme implementation.

	* view/workspace.py: Refactoring and Documentation
	
	* model/csound.py (_startCsoundOnMSW): 
		+ Bugfix: csound process output reapears on the calling console
	

2006-01-11  Sebastian Gutsfeld  <segoh@gmx.net>

	* view/controller.py (onMouseMotion): instead of showing the mouse
	coordinates in the statusbar show the instrument number of the
	module under point

	
